snippet.title: Self-Care Rx #2 - Nourishing Foods
snippet.description:
SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE: http://www.youtube.com/c/thespadr

Self-Care is an important foundation for true healthcare. And, it all starts with the foods we eat to nourish skin from the inside out. Dr. Cates shares her second Self-Care Prescription in the series.

To know more about Nourishing Foods please visit: https://thespadr.com/self-care-rx-food/
=================================================
#thespadr #nourishingfood #selfcare #tips
=================================================
👩‍⚕️ ABOUT DR TREVOR CATES
Dr. Trevor Cates is author of the USA Today and Amazon bestselling book Clean Skin From Within and founder of The Spa Dr. natural skin care line. She believes the key to healthy skin is inner and outer nourishment with natural and non-toxic ingredients.
